==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-expert.ogg|Audio (US)}}

=== Noun ===

# A person with extensive knowledge of a given subject.
#: ''We called in several experts on the subject, but they couldn't reach an agreement.''
# (''chess'') A ranking just below [[master]].

